1
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:27,560
Fourth Young Master!

2
00:01:28,200 --> 00:01:28,760
Fourth Young Master!

3
00:01:29,040 --> 00:01:30,040
You're finally back!

4
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:33,239
What's the rush?

5
00:01:33,719 --> 00:01:34,560
Did someone die in the manor?

6
00:01:34,719 --> 00:01:35,480
Fourth Young Master,

7
00:01:35,719 --> 00:01:36,959
you can't joke about that!

8
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:38,159
Today is the day of ancestral rites.

9
00:01:38,319 --> 00:01:38,959
The master said

10
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:39,879
once the Fourth Young Master returns,

11
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:41,079
head to the ancestral hall at once.

12
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:42,519
Understood.

13
00:01:51,319 --> 00:01:51,920
That's right.

14
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:53,760
Every year around this time,

15
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:56,599
every household in Da Xuan honors their ancestors.

16
00:01:57,319 --> 00:01:58,519
Since coming to this world,

17
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:00,599
I haven't once paid respects to Mother.

18
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:10,280
So you finally remembered to come back?

19
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:11,960
On the day of ancestral rites,

20
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:13,000
where have you been?

21
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:15,120
His Majesty summoned me.

22
00:02:15,719 --> 00:02:16,680
Go ask His Majesty yourself.

23
00:02:17,039 --> 00:02:18,000
What's all the shouting about?

24
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:19,879
You...

25
00:02:19,879 --> 00:02:20,319
Ning Chen!

26
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:22,039
What kind of attitude is that?

27
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:23,840
Before our ancestors' tablets,

28
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:25,360
how dare you be so disrespectful?

29
00:02:25,719 --> 00:02:26,360
Exactly.

30
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:27,479
No manners at all.

31
00:02:27,719 --> 00:02:29,759
Think being an Imperial Inspectorate

32
00:02:29,879 --> 00:02:31,000
Silver Robe lets you defy your elders?

33
00:02:31,159 --> 00:02:31,639
Exactly.

34
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:35,319
That temper of yours really needs to change.

35
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:36,800
With an attitude like that,

36
00:02:37,159 --> 00:02:39,400
people will call you a wild country brat

37
00:02:39,719 --> 00:02:40,599
with no manners.

38
00:02:41,039 --> 00:02:42,919
You'll bring shame to the Ning family.

39
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:44,159
Enough.

40
00:02:44,639 --> 00:02:46,000
Stop scolding him.

41
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:48,479
No one taught him growing up.

42
00:02:48,759 --> 00:02:50,199
It's only natural he lacks manners.

43
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:52,639
We can teach him in time.

44
00:03:09,599 --> 00:03:10,240
Lord Ning,

45
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:12,879
don't you think a tablet is missing here?

46
00:03:13,960 --> 00:03:14,960
Nonsense.

47
00:03:15,439 --> 00:03:16,520
We hold these rites every year.

48
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:18,240
Would I not know if one was missing?

49
00:03:18,639 --> 00:03:19,719
Where is my mother's tablet?

50
00:03:27,159 --> 00:03:27,719
Ning Chen!

51
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:29,240
What nonsense are you spouting?

52
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:31,400
This is the Ning family's ancestral hall.

53
00:03:31,919 --> 00:03:33,759
Your mother bore you out of wedlock.

54
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:35,319
What right has she to enter this hall?

55
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:37,800
Only the Ning matriarch may enter here.

56
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:39,599
Your mother was shameless,

57
00:03:39,919 --> 00:03:41,039
disgracing Father.

58
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,520
If Father hadn't taken pity on you,

59
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:44,520
you couldn't even enter the Ning gates.

60
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:46,280
And you want a tablet for your mother?

61
00:03:46,879 --> 00:03:47,719
Are you even worthy?

62
00:03:58,240 --> 00:03:59,000
Ning Ziming.

63
00:04:00,719 --> 00:04:02,319
My mother loved you her whole life.

64
00:04:03,879 --> 00:04:05,319
She waited for you her whole life.

65
00:04:07,319 --> 00:04:08,240
And you just calmly stand there

66
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:09,560
listening to your son insult her?

67
00:04:13,759 --> 00:04:15,599
I thought you were a beast,

68
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:19,800
but you're worse than a beast.

69
00:04:20,519 --> 00:04:21,279
You insolent wretch!

70
00:04:21,959 --> 00:04:23,439
How dare you curse your own father!

71
00:04:26,839 --> 00:04:28,279
Where are you going on this day of rites?

72
00:04:28,639 --> 00:04:29,839
You'll all find out soon enough.

73
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:40,240
Eldest Brother.

74
00:04:40,759 --> 00:04:42,639
Did you see the look on Ning Chen's face?

75
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:43,759
He was absolutely livid.

76
00:04:43,959 --> 00:04:44,959
Almost choked on his own rage.

77
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:47,439
He thinks being an Imperial Inspectorate

78
00:04:47,519 --> 00:04:49,000
Silver Robe means we can't touch him.

79
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:51,680
As long as we don't slip up,

80
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,680
and don't give him any leverage,

81
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:55,240
he can't do a thing to us.

82
00:04:56,639 --> 00:04:58,240
A lowly bastard born of a whore,

83
00:04:58,639 --> 00:05:01,040
yet he wants his mother in the shrine.

84
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:02,519
What a joke.

85
00:05:03,759 --> 00:05:04,480
Exactly.

86
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:05,519
Eldest Brother.

87
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:06,480
Eldest Brother, Second Brother,

88
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:08,079
look what I found!

89
00:05:13,959 --> 00:05:14,879
Whoa.

90
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:16,839
This is made of pure gold, isn't it?

91
00:05:17,639 --> 00:05:18,079
Eldest Brother,

92
00:05:18,519 --> 00:05:20,360
looks like that kid Ning Chen dropped it.

93
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:20,800
Right.

94
00:05:21,439 --> 00:05:24,160
He must have gotten it through bribery.

95
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:26,319
This is dozens of taels of gold.

96
00:05:26,879 --> 00:05:27,680
And these gemstones on it,

97
00:05:27,839 --> 00:05:28,920
are clearly worth a fortune.

98
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:31,199
Hide it first.

99
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:33,600
Last time at the music bureau,

100
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:35,480
that guy made me lose a jade flute.

101
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:36,959
Consider this my compensation.

102
00:05:37,639 --> 00:05:38,279
Eldest Brother! Eldest Brother!

103
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:42,879
Master! Madam!

104
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:43,879
Bad news!

105
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:45,879
Have you no manners, panicking like this?

106
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:48,800
F-Fourth Young Master brought men from the

107
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:49,639
Imperial Inspectorate and stormed in!

108
00:05:50,160 --> 00:05:50,720
What?

109
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:58,920
Lord Ning.

110
00:05:59,959 --> 00:06:00,959
Imperial Inspectorate, on official business.

111
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:03,680
All bystanders, stay where you are.

112
00:06:04,639 --> 00:06:05,360
Anyone who resists

113
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:07,600
will be killed on the spot.

114
00:06:08,759 --> 00:06:09,560
From this moment on,

115
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:11,120
for the entire Ning Manor,

116
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:12,560
only entry is allowed.

117
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:14,000
No one is allowed out.

118
00:06:18,279 --> 00:06:20,079
You unfilial son, what are you doing?

119
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:24,800
Lord Pan, let me tell you,

120
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:25,879
I am the Minister of Rites!

121
00:06:26,199 --> 00:06:27,800
You barge into my manor without cause,

122
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:28,879
what is the meaning of this?

123
00:06:29,639 --> 00:06:31,360
I'll petition His Majesty himself,

124
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:32,800
and you'll pay dearly for this!

125
00:06:34,079 --> 00:06:34,800
Lord Ning,

126
00:06:35,279 --> 00:06:36,120
when I entered the palace today,

127
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:37,839
His Majesty gifted me the imperial sword.

128
00:06:38,879 --> 00:06:40,560
I had it with me at the ancestral shrine.

129
00:06:41,199 --> 00:06:42,720
But now the imperial sword is gone.

130
00:06:43,759 --> 00:06:44,560
Tell me,

131
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:45,879
stealing the imperial sword,

132
00:06:47,319 --> 00:06:49,120
what is the penalty?

133
00:06:53,279 --> 00:06:54,519
Where's the sword?

134
00:06:59,279 --> 00:07:00,600
Speak up!

135
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:02,800
No, no, no!

136
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:03,680
I don't know, I don't know!

137
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:04,399
Guards!

138
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:07,879
Take them all to the Inspectorate.

139
00:07:08,199 --> 00:07:08,680
Yes, sir!

140
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:10,199
No, no!

141
00:07:10,839 --> 00:07:11,319
This...

142
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:11,959
Lord Pan!

143
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:12,639
Lord Ning,

144
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:14,120
whatever you have to say,

145
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,639
say it back at the Inspectorate.

146
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:17,959
After you.

147
00:07:35,759 --> 00:07:36,399
Fourth Brother

148
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:38,360
We know we were wrong

149
00:07:38,839 --> 00:07:40,319
Just let us out of here

150
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:41,040
Fourth Brother

151
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:43,160
You... you can't do this to us

152
00:07:43,519 --> 00:07:44,000
Ning Chen

153
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:46,360
I'm warning you, you'd better...

154
00:07:50,639 --> 00:07:51,439
Young masters

155
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:54,399
The Imperial Inspectorate's dungeon

156
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:55,800
Do you like it?

157
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:57,879
I asked you a question. Answer me.

158
00:08:01,079 --> 00:08:02,560
We like it

159
00:08:03,399 --> 00:08:04,000
Fourth Brother

160
00:08:04,639 --> 00:08:05,759
We're all family

161
00:08:06,079 --> 00:08:06,920
You can't do this

162
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:08,720
Family?

163
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:10,480
Who's your family?

164
00:08:10,759 --> 00:08:11,519
My mother's memorial tablet

165
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:13,120
isn't even allowed in your ancestral hall

166
00:08:14,319 --> 00:08:16,480
If Ning Ziming hadn't feared the shame

167
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:20,439
I couldn't even enter the Ning estate.

168
00:08:21,279 --> 00:08:22,480
The "bastard" you all called me,

169
00:08:23,279 --> 00:08:25,519
how could he ever be your family?

170
00:08:27,879 --> 00:08:29,360
You are young masters of the Ning estate.

171
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:30,800
Stop kneeling.

172
00:08:31,839 --> 00:08:33,120
I much prefer

173
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:34,720
seeing how you were in the ancestral hall,

174
00:08:35,759 --> 00:08:38,080
when you humiliated me and my mother,

175
00:08:39,039 --> 00:08:40,559
that arrogant, defiant look

176
00:08:42,559 --> 00:08:43,120
Get up

177
00:08:45,679 --> 00:08:46,159
Tie them up

178
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:47,159
Yes, sir

179
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:48,879
No, no

180
00:08:49,639 --> 00:08:50,080
No

181
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:50,840
This...

182
00:08:52,399 --> 00:08:53,279
Ning Chen, you...

183
00:09:14,759 --> 00:09:16,200
Fourth Brother Ning Chen, Fourth Brother

184
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:17,120
I'm begging you

185
00:09:17,399 --> 00:09:18,759
Please spare me

186
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:19,799
I swear

187
00:09:20,399 --> 00:09:21,759
I'll never bully you again

188
00:09:22,039 --> 00:09:23,639
A tiger on the plains is bullied by dogs.

189
00:09:24,159 --> 00:09:26,480
Scared now the tiger's back in the wild?

190
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:34,000
Fourth Brother

191
00:09:34,279 --> 00:09:35,000
No, no

192
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:36,320
Big Brother Four!

193
00:09:36,799 --> 00:09:37,840
I'll say it again

194
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:39,679
We are born of the same root.

195
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:41,480
Why so quick to...

196
00:09:43,039 --> 00:09:43,639
Quick?

197
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:45,000
There's no rush this time.

198
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:47,519
Fourth Brother

199
00:09:47,799 --> 00:09:49,320
We're brothers, after all

200
00:09:49,679 --> 00:09:51,039
Blood is thicker than water

201
00:09:51,399 --> 00:09:53,039
We should be standing together

202
00:09:55,039 --> 00:09:56,320
By age,

203
00:09:56,559 --> 00:09:58,080
you're actually our eldest brother

204
00:09:58,320 --> 00:09:59,799
The eldest son of the household

205
00:10:00,399 --> 00:10:00,919
Yes

206
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:02,200
You're the eldest brother

207
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:03,399
You are truly the eldest brother

208
00:10:03,679 --> 00:10:05,320
Now you know to call me "eldest brother"?

209
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:06,080
Eldest Brother

210
00:10:06,559 --> 00:10:07,360
Eldest Brother, Eldest Brother

211
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:07,919
Eldest Brother

212
00:10:18,679 --> 00:10:19,600
Ning Chen.

213
00:10:20,559 --> 00:10:22,120
You're convicting us on your own,

214
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:23,360
carrying out illegal punishments,

215
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:26,120
violating the laws of the realm.

216
00:10:26,559 --> 00:10:27,240
And another thing.

217
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:31,120
You planted that sword there on purpose?

218
00:10:35,039 --> 00:10:35,639
Take a guess.

219
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:38,440
I never thought a bastard like you

220
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:40,120
could hide so well.

221
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:43,600
I should never have let you live.

222
00:10:44,919 --> 00:10:46,399
Regretting it now?

223
00:10:48,279 --> 00:10:49,799
But don't get too smug.

224
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:51,480
Grandfather is the Left Chancellor.

225
00:10:51,879 --> 00:10:53,759
He will surely come to save us.

226
00:10:54,559 --> 00:10:56,759
Either you finish me off today,

227
00:10:57,279 --> 00:10:57,759
or else,

228
00:10:58,360 --> 00:10:59,320
in the future,

229
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:02,960
I'll repay this humiliation a hundredfold.

230
00:11:09,879 --> 00:11:11,879
I love helping people get what they want.

231
00:11:14,639 --> 00:11:15,080
Ning Chen.

232
00:11:15,559 --> 00:11:16,679
What are you doing?

233
00:11:17,559 --> 00:11:18,320
This thing

234
00:11:18,600 --> 00:11:20,639
is used on female criminals.

235
00:11:20,799 --> 00:11:21,279
You're using it on him...

236
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:22,399
You mustn't.

237
00:11:22,639 --> 00:11:23,639
Absolutely must not.

238
00:11:24,159 --> 00:11:24,679
Chen.

239
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:25,919
Are you really going to use that thing

240
00:11:26,159 --> 00:11:27,639
on where they relieve themselves?

241
00:11:28,279 --> 00:11:29,879
That's something I couldn't bear to watch.

242
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:31,919
Too horrible to behold.

243
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:33,399
Blood gushing everywhere.

244
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:34,960
Blood gushing everywhere.

245
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:37,799
Wouldn't that be perfect?

246
00:11:38,559 --> 00:11:40,000
Pure ecstasy.

247
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:42,519
A soul-shattering experience.

248
00:11:43,519 --> 00:11:47,600
A unique taste to savor.

249
00:12:21,759 --> 00:12:22,679
What are you staring at?

250
00:12:22,679 --> 00:12:23,360
Help out!

251
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:24,559
Come on, come on.

252
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:27,840
No, no, no!

253
00:12:28,399 --> 00:12:29,600
Get ready, get ready.

254
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:30,279
Come on, come on.

255
00:12:30,279 --> 00:12:31,480
I can't, I really can't!

256
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:32,320
Come on.

257
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:32,799
Wait a moment!

258
00:12:33,679 --> 00:12:34,120
Wait a moment!

259
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:36,559
Fourth Brother.

260
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:37,360
No.

261
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:38,759
Fourth Brother.

262
00:12:39,879 --> 00:12:40,759
Big Fourth Brother.

263
00:12:40,879 --> 00:12:41,960
I... I don't want to die.

264
00:12:41,960 --> 00:12:42,600
Spare me, please.

265
00:12:42,639 --> 00:12:43,840
I'm begging you, spare me!

266
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:44,919
We're family.

267
00:12:44,919 --> 00:12:45,360
Do you remember?

268
00:12:45,360 --> 00:12:46,399
We're family.

269
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:47,480
I'm begging you.

270
00:12:47,480 --> 00:12:48,399
Please let me go.

271
00:12:48,399 --> 00:12:49,320
I don't want to die.

272
00:12:50,759 --> 00:12:51,440
Fine then.

273
00:12:53,240 --> 00:12:54,240
Since that's the case,

274
00:12:54,440 --> 00:12:55,240
I'll give you a chance.

275
00:12:55,240 --> 00:12:55,720
Alright.

276
00:12:57,360 --> 00:12:58,159
Listen carefully.

277
00:12:58,960 --> 00:13:00,399
Which of you has met the Poison Lord?

278
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:03,919
The what Lord?

279
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:05,679
Whose Lord?

280
00:13:11,320 --> 00:13:12,200
You've seen him, haven't you?

281
00:13:12,840 --> 00:13:14,039
And at the Left Chancellor's manor.

282
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:17,000
No, I...

283
00:13:17,399 --> 00:13:19,080
I don't know what you're talking about.

284
00:13:19,960 --> 00:13:22,240
Second Brother, just tell him already!

285
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:26,240
Ning Gan, oh Ning Gan.

286
00:13:26,639 --> 00:13:28,440
What's the point of holding out?

287
00:13:31,039 --> 00:13:33,720
The Poison Lord is a key wanted fugitive.

288
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:36,799
If you take the fall for the Chancellor,

289
00:13:37,759 --> 00:13:39,279
no one will be able to protect you.

290
00:13:40,159 --> 00:13:42,120
But if you tell the truth today,

291
00:13:42,679 --> 00:13:45,639
I guarantee I'll send you safely home.

292
00:13:49,600 --> 00:13:50,200
I...

293
00:13:52,360 --> 00:13:54,360
I have no idea what you're talking about.

294
00:13:55,159 --> 00:13:56,080
Come on, come on, come on.

295
00:13:56,240 --> 00:13:56,759
Come on, come on.

296
00:13:56,960 --> 00:13:57,399
Get ready.

297
00:13:57,519 --> 00:13:58,840
No, no, no! Come on, come on.

298
00:13:58,960 --> 00:13:59,559
Come on.

299
00:13:59,720 --> 00:14:00,399
Help!

300
00:14:00,440 --> 00:14:00,919
Wait a moment!

301
00:14:04,440 --> 00:14:05,879
Help! Help!

302
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:07,360
You few, get over here.

303
00:14:09,320 --> 00:14:09,720
Sit down.

304
00:14:10,480 --> 00:14:11,080
Behave yourselves.

305
00:14:25,720 --> 00:14:26,399
Knock it off.

306
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:27,679
Let him go.

307
00:14:29,159 --> 00:14:29,600
Wait...

308
00:14:31,320 --> 00:14:32,279
Old Pan, what are you saying?

309
00:14:33,120 --> 00:14:34,639
Ning Gan must know where Poison Lord is.

310
00:14:35,440 --> 00:14:36,720
The Poison Lord is already dead.

311
00:14:37,200 --> 00:14:38,879
The Left Chancellor delivered his body.

312
00:14:43,480 --> 00:14:44,200
Just like that,

313
00:14:44,559 --> 00:14:45,840
he's even cleared of suspicion.

314
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:47,519
He gets credit for catching the bandits.

315
00:14:49,879 --> 00:14:51,679
What a brilliant turning of the tables.

316
00:14:52,120 --> 00:14:52,879
Brothers,

317
00:14:55,320 --> 00:14:57,120
to bring down a towering tree

318
00:14:57,799 --> 00:14:58,600
isn't that simple.

319
00:14:59,360 --> 00:15:00,639
We must have a sharp weapon in hand,

320
00:15:01,360 --> 00:15:02,240
to sever its branches and leaves,

321
00:15:02,440 --> 00:15:03,200
and chop down its roots.

322
00:15:04,080 --> 00:15:05,440
We're about to march out soon.

323
00:15:05,799 --> 00:15:07,639
Military merit is our finest weapon.

324
00:15:13,639 --> 00:15:15,279
You two, stop standing around.

325
00:15:16,519 --> 00:15:17,159
Let him go.
